  "body": "# Bug Report\n\n## Problem\nIn case of incoming transaction balance is not updated until reopening app (for fresh accounts only. pull to refresh, put app to background don't help)\nAfter that balance is updating normally.\nReproducible on Ropsten and mainnet for fresh accounts.\nThe issue appeared in nightly 12/03.\nIt is reason of failing 3 e2e in nightly.\n\n#### Expected behavior\nBalance is updated\n\n#### Actual behavior\nBalance is the same.\n![ezgif com-video-to-gif (2)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/77061814-2653c580-69db-11ea-8bae-a554c19817a1.gif)\n\n\n\n### Reproduction\n\n\n- Open Status\n- Switch to Ropsten\n- Open Status Test Dapp and request ETH (skip faucet request error)\n- When transaction appears, pay attention to balance\n\n### Additional Information\n\n- Status version: nightly 12/03\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\n\n#### Logs\n\n[status_logs_b.zip](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/4354115/status_logs_b.zip)",
